Package: out2text
Title: Extract Outputs From Common Analyses and Convert Them To Text
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Shu Fai",
           family = "Cheung",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "shufai.cheung@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9871-9448")))
Description: Extract values such as regression coefficients, p-values,
             confidence intervals, from common procedures such as regression
             and format them as strings so that they can be embedded in
             RMarkdown or Quarto documents.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
